{"title":"英姿峭直","authors":["管桦"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"英姿峭直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管桦诗并画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你诞生在壮丽的河川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的湖岸，诞生在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵延无尽的峰峦之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和无边沉雄大地的深处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在飞舞的烟云中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身披着绿色甲胄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒霜飞雪之所激，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风骤雨之所撼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天崩地裂之所震，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英姿峭直入太苍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊不朽的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在时代的风雨中呼啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在闪电的亮光里闪耀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是我歌唱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你高风亮节的情操品德，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你云水襟怀莽原气概。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱你碧叶萧萧扫腐浊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青竿如剑斩毒虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让竹林充满清光、清气、清风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱你灵魂色调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同大自然色调的融合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从大自然深谷发出的回声。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":14,"page_end":14}